{% blocktrans count candy_num=4 %}
  {{ candy_num }} candy
{% plural %}
  {{ candy_num }} candies
{% endblocktrans %}
```

Result:

`'candy_num' is undefined`

In `extensions.py`:

```python
            if context is None:
                return ugettext(force_text(singular)) % trans_vars
            else:
                return pgettext(force_text(context), force_text(singular)) % trans_vars
        else:
            if context is None:
                return ungettext(
                    force_text(singular), force_text(plural), trans_vars[count_var] ...
